# Brain Training Site Implementation Plan

## Goal Description
Build a "Brain Training" web application using Node.js. The application will feature a "Memory Match" game to start, designed with a premium, modern aesthetic.
The stack will be **Node.js (Express)** for the backend and **React (Vite)** for the frontend.

## User Review Required
> [!NOTE]
> I am proposing **React + Vite** for the frontend to ensure a responsive and interactive gaming experience, and **Vanilla CSS** for styling to maintain full control over the "premium" aesthetic as per system guidelines.
> The backend will be **Express.js** to serve the application and handle potential future API needs (like high scores).

